# Sales & Profit Performance Dashboard

A comprehensive Business Intelligence portfolio project analyzing transactional orders and customer data to evaluate revenue streams, regional profitability, and product category performance.

## 📊 Project Overview
This project transforms raw data into an interactive, decision-support dashboard using **Power BI Desktop**, **SQL**, and **Excel**. It demonstrates end-to-end data modeling, relationship mapping, custom metric calculation via **DAX**, and modern dashboard design principles.

### Key Visualizations & Features
* **Executive KPI Cards:** High-level summaries tracking **Total Revenue**, **Total Profit**, and overall **Profit Margin**.
* **Global Date Slicer:** Dynamic filtering allowing users to instantly slice the entire dashboard by specific years (2025, 2026).
* **Revenue Trend Analysis:** A smoothed line chart tracking monthly revenue growth trajectories over time.
* **Regional Profitability Breakdown:** A clustered bar chart identifying top-performing and underperforming geographic territories.
* **Customer Segmentation:** A donut chart analyzing sales distribution across consumer types.
* **Granular Category Matrix:** A detailed table breaking down Sales, Profit, and Profit Margins across product categories (Furniture, Office Supplies, Technology).

